modName: Alex a Female Nord Preset (Mods required)
summary: This is a female nord that I created with lots of different mods. Took a lot of time to get things perfect.
descriptionHtml:
So here are the required mods:

Tools:
SKSE
http://skse.silverlock.org/
SkyUI
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/3863/?
RaceMenu
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/29624//?
Enhanced Character Edit
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/12951/?
CharGen Extension
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/36925/?

Optional Models/Textures:
The Eyes of Beauty
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?
CBBE
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2666/?
UNP
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/6709/?
Sporty Sexy Sweat
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/28946/?

Hairs:
SG Hairs 120
I don't know where I got it. But it was from google. I can't find it anymore... and im pretty sure I shouldn't release it to the public because... well its not my mod. Sorry about that guys.

ENB: 
Cinemascope Performance ENB
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/15425/?


Thats it...
Don't forget to endorse if you like it

Instructions on how to get the preset:
1. Download those mods
2. Download my preset
3. Place the preset at data/skse/plugins/chargen/presets
4. Open up Skyrim (SKSE)
5. When in the character creation (or shawracemenu) go to the "preset slot" option and go to preset 0.
6. Press f9
7. ???
8. Profit.
author: General Currystador
